5
00:00:31,031 --> 00:00:32,157
FORLADT BARN

6
00:00:32,240 --> 00:00:33,908
<i>...fanget i et skyggeland.</i>

7
00:00:37,746 --> 00:00:39,247
<i>En verden af hvisken,</i>

8
00:00:40,040 --> 00:00:43,084
