11
00:00:51,051 --> 00:00:52,302
STANFORD UNIVERSITET

12
00:00:53,178 --> 00:00:55,597
LUCKY B BØRNEHJEM

13
00:00:58,808 --> 00:01:00,101
<i>Men med ensomhed...</i>

14
00:01:02,395 --> 00:01:03,605
